; G_CTLZ_ZERO_POISON / G_CTTZ_ZERO_POISON and the clamp disappears.
;
; GCN           = combine enabled  (this PR)  -> no v_min_u32 32 clamp
; GCN-NOCOMBINE = combine disabled (baseline) -> v_min_u32 32 clamp present

